# ppx_enforce rules for Miaou widget libraries
# Every widget .ml file must self-register in Miaou_registry so tools like
# the MCP server can discover the full widget API at runtime.
call Miaou_registry.register "Widget must self-register: add 'let () = Miaou_registry.register ~name:\"<name>\" ~mli:[%blob \"<file>.mli\"] ()' at the end of this file"
